-A PREROUTING  -p tcp -m tcp --dport 80 -j REDIRECT --to-ports 8080
COMMIT
*filter
:INPUT ACCEPT [17530:11182020]
:FORWARD ACCEPT [0:0]
:OUTPUT ACCEPT [22144:10946588]
